c', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/129046/', '', 'Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Secukinumab, Ravulizumab, Mycophenolic acid, Abatacept, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, Belumosudil, Thalidomide, Belimumab, Emapalumab, More', 'Entrectinib, Imatinib, Dabrafenib, Asciminib, Acalabrutinib, Dacomitinib, Pacritinib, Tepotinib, Fedratinib, Avapritinib, Larotrectinib, More', 1767369485);
